{
  "id": "adv_card_mna_52_01",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 1話 普段と違ーう！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月のテンペストのライブ数日前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days before Moon Tempest’s live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……もうすぐ月ストのライブ当日か\nまさか、麻奈の誕生日にライブとはなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It’s almost the day of the Moon Tempest live.\nTo think there’d be a live on Mana’s birthday…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、あの時のバースデーライブと同じ会場だなんて\nあいつが知ったら、なんて言うかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And at the same venue as that birthday live back then…\nI wonder what she’d say if she knew…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もっちろん、私もゲストで出るからね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I’d be appearing as a guest too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.0029246409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-09.m4a",
      "text": "全世界がずっと待ってた姉妹共演だもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The whole world has been waiting for this sisters’ duet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7562601169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……なんて言いそうだよなぁ\nまぁ、今回はゲストとして、遙子さんが出るんだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ that sounds like something she’d say.\nWell‚ this time‚ Haruko-san will be the guest instead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9333344778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈の誕生日に――\n琴乃のライブに、遙子さんが出るのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On Mana’s birthday—\nHaruko-san will be appearing at Kotono’s live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9000011445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――2017年",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The year 2017",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.759594218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 41.9262593587
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-03.m4a",
      "text": "会場、押さえられたって本当！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it true you reserved the venue!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.7929260969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、本当だ\n今年は出来るぞ、長瀬麻奈バースデーライブ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it’s true.\nThis year we can finally do it—Nagase Mana’s birthday live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6666678112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-08.m4a",
      "text": "やったー！　ありがとう{user}くん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay! Thank you‚ {user}-kun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5338566382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_thank-01.m4a",
      "text": "もう、去年からずーっとずーーっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ever since last year‚ I’ve been wanting and wanting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2338578302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-04.m4a",
      "text": "ずーーーーっと、やりたかったから、嬉しい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For so——— long! I’m so happy I finally can!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9338594356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "本当に出来るんだぁ、バースデーライブ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So it’s really happening… a birthday live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3405267378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなにやりたかったのか？　デビューしてまだ一年と\n少しだし、誕生日とはいえ大がかりなことは出来ないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You wanted it that badly? It’s only been about a year since your debut‚\nand even if it’s your birthday‚ we can’t do anything too big.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6333324432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-08.m4a",
      "text": "チッチッチ！　分かってないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tsk tsk! You don’t get it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.2927039382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "去年、私がどれだけ歯がゆい思いをしたかを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you know how frustrated I was last year?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.6527055583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-03.m4a",
      "text": "たまたま私の誕生日にライブがあったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ there was a live on my birthday by chance‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2260423578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いつも通りの普通のライブだったでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but it was just an ordinary live‚ wasn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.4527004636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "スタッフさん達がケーキを運んで来てくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The staff brought out a cake‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.9260367629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-08.m4a",
      "text": "私もそれでようやく誕生日だって思い出したくらいでさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and that’s when I finally remembered it was my birthday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2260368477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-11.m4a",
      "text": "会場のファンのみんなも、一緒になって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fans at the venue joined in‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2260367629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お祝いしてくれて、凄く嬉しかったんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and celebrated with me‚ which made me really happy‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.1333354949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-02.m4a",
      "text": "この麻奈ちゃんの誕生日だよ！？　ほんとはみんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was my birthday‚ you know!? Deep down‚ everyone must have",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.392717671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もーっと気合いを入れてお祝いしたかったはず！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "wanted to celebrate with waaay more spirit!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3793879956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そういうものか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-Is that how it is…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5260535475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-05.m4a",
      "text": "そういうものだよ！　私だって、今まで応援してくれた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s exactly how it is! I want to properly thank",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.3918810284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みんなに、しっかり感謝を伝えたいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "everyone who’s supported me all this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.1252184988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "誕生日って、私だけじゃなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Birthdays aren’t just about me—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.5585431173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-07.m4a",
      "text": "応援してくれてる人達にとっても特別なはずだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "they should be special for the people cheering for me too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5852163312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だからね！　今年は絶対絶対",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why! This year I really‚ really",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.9585548158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-15.m4a",
      "text": "バースデーライブがやりたかったの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "wanted to have a birthday live!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.2918763793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな。麻奈にとっても、ファンの人達にとっても\n日頃の感謝を伝えられる、特別な一日ってことか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. So for both you and the fans‚\nit’s a special day to express gratitude.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.1666790009,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（そしてそれは、俺達星見プロみんなの思いでもある）\n（今年は最高のステージを麻奈に贈るんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And that’s the same wish we at Hoshimi Pro all share.）\n（This year‚ we’ll give Mana the best stage.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.4000123342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
