      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-08.m4a",
      "text": "会場のみんなにも私の誕生日ケーキを分けたいなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to share my birthday cake with everyone at the venue!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 311.4144538237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "そんなサイズのケーキ……もはや、どんな大きさに\nなるのか想像もつかないが……まぁいいか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A cake that size… I can’t even imagine\nhow big it would have to be… but oh well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 319.9334779099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-05.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり何か企んでるでしょ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re definitely plotting something‚ aren’t you!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 324.4077636157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "リアクションが普段と違ーう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your reaction is not like usual!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 328.2410869513,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-01.m4a",
      "text": "なんてね。その様子だと、会場を押さえながら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just kidding. But from the look of things‚ while securing the venue—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 331.2744526618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "企画ももう、ある程度進行はしてるんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve already been moving forward with the plans‚ haven’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 335.4811153166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "まいったな……麻奈はなんでもお見通しか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m beat… Mana sees right through everything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 340.3411315355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-04.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ないなぁ、私のアイデアは来年に取っておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fine then‚ I’ll save my ideas for next year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 344.822061085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_thanks-03.m4a",
      "text": "やりたいこと、聞いてくれようとしてありがとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for at least trying to hear me out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 349.1666811626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-03.m4a",
      "text": "ある程度企画が固まったら私にも教えて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once the plans are set to some degree‚ tell me too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 353.2553923838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それで、実現出来そうな案があったら加えさせて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And if there’s an idea that seems doable‚ let me add it in?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 357.4220391427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-03.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、一つだけ！　遙子ちゃんにゲスト出演を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ just one thing! Could you ask Haruko-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 361.4220468436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "頼んだり出来ないかな？　お願いしてみていい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to appear as a guest? Can I try asking her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 365.6887038463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh021.m4a",
      "text": "いや……それは俺の方からも頼んだんだが\n遠慮するって言ってたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… I asked her myself too‚ but—\nshe said she’d decline.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 374.0334901168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……そっか。……うん、分かった。じゃあ、任せる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see. …Alright‚ I’ll leave it to you then!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 376.1097713065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
